---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL || "/";
---

<footer class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-400 border-t border-slate-800/50">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
			<div class="md:col-span-2">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-5">
					<span class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">OpenClaw</span>
				</div>
				<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-md text-slate-500">
					Mac Mini 環境構築サービス。現役セキュリティエンジニアによるセキュアで最適な業務環境の構築。
				</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-5">サービス</h4>
				<ul class="space-y-3.5">
					<li><a href="#service" class="no-underline text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-brand transition-colors">サービス内容</a></li>
					<li><a href="#features" class="no-underline text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-brand transition-colors">選ばれる理由</a></li>
					<li><a href="#flow" class="no-underline text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-brand transition-colors">導入フロー</a></li>
					<li><a href={`${base}contact`} class="no-underline text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-brand transition-colors">お問い合わせ</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-5">サポート</h4>
				<ul class="space-y-3.5">
					<li><a href="#faq" class="no-underline text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-brand transition-colors">よくある質問</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-14 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800/50 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
			<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">© {new Date().getFullYear()} OpenClaw. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
